lead_paragraph: Curtis Granderson stepped to the plate in a bottom of the ninth inning he never expected to see, surprised Jeurys Familia had blown a four-run lead.

headline.print_headline: Granderson's Homer in 9th Leads Mets Over Dodgers 6-5
